			How do you check-in <br> and check-out of an assignment?
		</h3>
		<hr>
		<p>
			When you're ready to check-in to your assignment, click on either "In Progress" or "Assigned" from the home page.
		</p>
		<p>
			Click on the title of the assignment and scroll down until you see the Check-in (or Check-out) button and click it.
			You can also do this from tapping the navigation icon at the top right of your screen or by swiping from right to left
			on your phone.
		</p>
